{"tid":2331272,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"政府: 世衞年初已有「2019冠狀病毒病」命名 傳媒表述不應以「武肺」污名化","createTime":"2020-12-18T15:55:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-20T05:23:20.000Z","uid":240362,"like":5,"dislike":109,"uniUserReply":97,"replies":[{"pid":"6d68a53ef74865dd71fcbfe24eb92a39c9d804a9","tid":2331272,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T15:55:15.000Z","msg":"政府回應查詢時表示，有需要提醒出席採訪政府活動的傳媒代表留意提問時的表述，指世衞組織已經於年初有「2019冠狀病毒病」的命名，傳媒代表的表述不應污名化。<br />\n<br />\n政府發言人引述世衞指，為病毒妥善命名很重要，有助防止使用其他可能不準確或污名化的名稱。<br />\n<br />\n衞生防護中心舉行疫情記者會期間，有傳媒發問時以「武肺」形容新型肺炎，主持記者會的新聞主任提示記者，可以採用「新冠病毒」的字眼，其後另有記者再追問日後發問時採用「武漢肺炎」字眼，是否違法以及會否失去發問機會。<br />\n<br />\n政府回覆本台查詢時，並無回應由哪個部門提出要注意傳媒提問時的表述，以及繼續採用「武漢肺炎」的字眼有何後果。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1566112-20201218.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1566112-20201218.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=FaFb5890SAgm9tgOvLsHBS3KoYHjImyLH66vjnFGY4M%3D&h=3647b309\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1566112-20201218.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=d4fcc273\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1566112-20201218.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"02573670b39d01972552311c3e2be53be844efc9","tid":2331272,"uid":317228,"like":48,"dislike":0,"score":48,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T15:56:03.000Z","msg":"支那武漢肺炎"},{"pid":"a1870fbebfcc9e914205565e3a776c11a2772551","tid":2331272,"uid":79117,"like":42,"dislike":1,"score":41,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T15:56:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9336cc8a648d40738001d911eb5528f0b60a67bf","tid":2331272,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T15:56:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/gun.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/gun.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/gun.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb852da3c750faff139b543e1564fe3245ab953d","tid":2331272,"uid":79563,"like":93,"dislike":0,"score":93,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T15:57:46.000Z","msg":"咁你又叫人<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">尼泊爾病毒株</span></span></strong>去污名化尼泊爾？"},{"pid":"2829bed71cfa321d8966d1355d745ddd9df07913","tid":2331272,"uid":247845,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T15:58:09.000Z","msg":"簡稱武肺"},{"pid":"700fb2c7883de73144891953d0299b35b91071ee","tid":2331272,"uid":156913,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T15:59:12.000Z","msg":"新冠病毒 武漢肺炎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18b241d5397362c68134fb2106dafb06ce95fa56","tid":2331272,"uid":50386,"like":70,"dislike":0,"score":70,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T16:06:48.000Z","msg":"德國麻疹，中東呼吸綜合症，日本腦炎，<br />\n札榥病毒，西尼羅河病毒，伊波拉病毒，<br />\n呢啲「污名化」嘅名仲響衛生防護中心搵到<br />\n就係武漢肺炎唔講得<br />\n<br />\n總之全世界都可以污名化，係支那唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.chp.gov.hk/tc/healthtopics/content/24/40.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chp.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fhealthtopics%2Fcontent%2F24%2F40.html&d=FaFb5890SAgm9tgOvLsHBS3KoYHjImyLH66vjnFGY4M%3D&h=470a2a2c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.chp.gov.hk/tc/healthtopics/content/24/40.html</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.chp.gov.hk/tc/healthtopics/content/24/26528.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chp.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fhealthtopics%2Fcontent%2F24%2F26528.html&d=FaFb5890SAgm9tgOvLsHBS3KoYHjImyLH66vjnFGY4M%3D&h=ebf23180\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.chp.gov.hk/tc/healthtopics/content/24/26528.html</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.chp.gov.hk/tc/healthtopics/content/24/28.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chp.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fhealthtopics%2Fcontent%2F24%2F28.html&d=FaFb5890SAgm9tg